title: Cause For Alarm!  (MKV)
description:
Not Rated | 1h 14min | Crime, Drama, Film-Noir | August 23rd 1951



Mr. Jones is a husband who wrongly thinks his wife and doctor are conspiring to kill him and outlines that suspicion in letter, which causes a serious concern when he ends up dying anyway.


Director: Tay Garnett

Writers: Mel Dinelli (screenplay), Tom Lewis (screenplay)

Stars: Loretta Young, Barry Sullivan, Bruce Cowling



English audio
